"Who are we?"  (you me, the rest of us)  
"What are we doing?"  (agents or action)  
"Are we even together?"  (this is you, this is me, ..)  

Hey, you probably know who I am - or atleast have an idea of who you think I am. Some combination of what you are told, what you have read, a little bit of gossip, and it your really on to me then you may have even met me (in which case, thanks for tolerating me)

Anyways, let's get back to the topic at hand.  

We are quite a pair, you and I. Who we are as individuals